        {
            "title": "日本首相高市早苗的追加預算規模據悉將達1120億美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"598\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/cG2UpwN5yF4Iq3wv7BCkHg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU5ODtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/1457c60562bd8933f216d41263e11364\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 日本首相高市早苗將公佈一項經濟方案，作為該方案資金來源的追加預算，比前任首相在一年前支出計畫中承諾的規模高出約27%，凸顯了她對擴張性財政政策的堅定。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據彭博周四看到的文件顯示，該方案將包含來自一般賬戶中的17.7萬億日圓（1120億美元）的支出。預計該方案將整合減稅和從特別賬戶中提取的支出。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這超過了前首相石破茂在去年公佈的13.9萬億日圓，而且實際上將是即將宣布的追加預算規模。知情人士稱，鑒於預算規模擴大，新增債券發行量也將高於去年。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-63c6b0d1-e81d-3b45-b2fc-e96239aefc9e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">文件顯示，該方案總規模（包括一些已列入預算的項目）將達到21.3萬億日圓。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本財務省未立即回覆置評請求。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"598\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/gg_MPyQkcDv_LA.q1IKsaA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU5ODtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/e0e1e3a2e13d9f4c4eca661be7d3992c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">加上私營部門的支出，預計該方案的整體規模效應將達到約42.8萬億日圓，政府希望藉此應對持續通膨、安全風險等一系列挑戰。本周早些時候公佈的數據顯示，截至9月的三個月，日本實際國內生產毛額按年率計算萎縮1.8%，為六個季度以來的首次下降，也讓高市政府更有理由加大支出力度。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">一般賬戶支出增加將需要更大的追加預算，其中包括增發政府債券，這將加劇債務負擔。對債務水平上升的擔憂推動日本5年期和10年期國債殖利率在周四早些時候升至2008年以來的最高水平。日圓兌美元跌破157，創下1月以來的最弱。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Japan’s Takaichi Is Set to Unveil $112 Billion in Fresh Stimulus</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%A6%96%E7%9B%B8%E9%AB%98%E5%B8%82%E6%97%A9%E8%8B%97%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%BD%E5%8A%A0%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E5%B0%87%E9%81%941120%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-074918790.html",
